          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-235-37L1-line-1" n="1">
              <hi rend="display-initial">B<hi rend="small-caps">ENEATH</hi> this verdant hillock lies</hi>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-37L1-line-2" n="2"><hi rend="italics">Demar</hi>, the wealthy and the wise.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-37L1-line-3" n="3">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-37L1-line-4" n="4">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-37L1-line-5" n="5">His heirs, that he might safely rest,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-37L1-line-6" n="6">Have put his carcass in a chest:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-37L1-line-7" n="7">The very chest, in which, they say,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-37L1-line-8" n="8">His other self, his money, lay.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-37L1-line-9" n="9">And if his heirs continue kind</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-37L1-line-10" n="10">To that dear self he left behind,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-37L1-line-11" n="11">I dare believe, that four in five</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-37L1-line-12" n="12">Will think his better half alive.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
